snippet.title: Trojan gameplay (PC Game, 1986)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Trojan, Dos PC game produced by Capcom in 1986 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/trojan/8311/
Trojan is an interesting action game, created in the mid 80's. Your character is equipped with both a sword and must kill many enemies. This game can also play multiplayer. Good luck. .
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
